FBIS4-45461 "jptdd027__l94039" JPRS-TDD-94-027L JPRS Narcotics 14 June 1994 EAST ASIA VIETNAM Drug Addicts in Lao Cai Receiving Medical Treatment Drug Addicts in Lao Cai Receiving Medical Treatment BK1506100694 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 2300 GMT 14 Jun 94 BK1506100694 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network Vietnamese BFN [Text] In cooperation with the Drug Rehabilitation Center of Bao Thang District, the Lao Cai public health sector has since October 1993 given medical treatment to 123 drug addicts. They have reported for treatment in a voluntary and compulsory manner. Nearly sixty percent of the patients have been cured and they have been sent back to rejoin their communities.
